{
    "poem_title": "Neige",
    "author": "Théodore de Banville",
    "structure": "suite périodique",
    "year": "1888",
    "manually_checked": false,
    "stanzas": [
        {
            "stanza_number": 1,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 1,
                    "line_text": "La neige tombe en flocons",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "line_text": "Sur les toits, sur les balcons.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "line_text": "C'est à se croire en Norvège.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Les gazons gèlent, tapis",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Sous un merveilleux tapis.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Car il neige, il neige, il neige.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "La neige tombe en flocons\nSur les toits, sur les balcons.\nC'est à se croire en Norvège.\nLes gazons gèlent, tapis\nSous un merveilleux tapis.\nCar il neige, il neige, il neige."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Pour combiner, en ses jeux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Un effet de blanc neigeux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Le ciel a jeté ses perles.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Mais ces parures de cour",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Sont un mince régal, pour",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Les moineaux et pour les merles.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Pour combiner, en ses jeux,\nUn effet de blanc neigeux,\nLe ciel a jeté ses perles.\nMais ces parures de cour\nSont un mince régal, pour\nLes moineaux et pour les merles."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Par ce temps, ils n'errent pas.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Mais enfin, pour quel repas",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Cette nappe est-elle mise ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "La Terre, montrant son flanc,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Est dans un vêtement blanc,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Comme une dame en chemise.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Par ce temps, ils n'errent pas.\nMais enfin, pour quel repas\nCette nappe est-elle mise ?\nLa Terre, montrant son flanc,\nEst dans un vêtement blanc,\nComme une dame en chemise."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Or, mesdames, le rimeur",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Se livre à sa belle humeur,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Et sur les routes divines",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Aux harmonieux dessins,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Voit les blancheurs de vos seins",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Et celles de vos poitrines.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Or, mesdames, le rimeur\nSe livre à sa belle humeur,\nEt sur les routes divines\nAux harmonieux dessins,\nVoit les blancheurs de vos seins\nEt celles de vos poitrines."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Sous la neige ensevelis,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Mais levant leurs fronts pâlis",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Que le vent ne peut abattre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Les arbres un peu tremblants,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Ont tous des panaches blancs,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Comme le roi Henri Quatre.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Sous la neige ensevelis,\nMais levant leurs fronts pâlis\nQue le vent ne peut abattre,\nLes arbres un peu tremblants,\nOnt tous des panaches blancs,\nComme le roi Henri Quatre."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "Les petits dos féminins",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Sont comme des Apennins ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "Et Flavie, Emma, Nadège,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Pour qui j'enfle mes pipeaux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "Sur leurs élégants chapeaux",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "Emportent des fleurs de neige.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Les petits dos féminins\nSont comme des Apennins ;\nEt Flavie, Emma, Nadège,\nPour qui j'enfle mes pipeaux,\nSur leurs élégants chapeaux\nEmportent des fleurs de neige."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "Des loups, terreur des marmots,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "Pénètrent dans les hameaux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "Plus sérieux que des mages,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "Et si j'en crois le journal,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "On en voit dans Épinal,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "Où se vendent les images.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Des loups, terreur des marmots,\nPénètrent dans les hameaux,\nPlus sérieux que des mages,\nEt si j'en crois le journal,\nOn en voit dans Épinal,\nOù se vendent les images."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "Ces loups, fuyant nos paris,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 44,
                    "line_text": "Ne viennent pas à Paris.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 45,
                    "line_text": "Mais dans ce Paris, qui m'aime",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 46,
                    "line_text": "Et qui, malgré les méchants,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 47,
                    "line_text": "Écoute parfois nos chants,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 48,
                    "line_text": "Nous en avons tout de même.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ces loups, fuyant nos paris,\nNe viennent pas à Paris.\nMais dans ce Paris, qui m'aime\nEt qui, malgré les méchants,\nÉcoute parfois nos chants,\nNous en avons tout de même."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 9,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 49,
                    "line_text": "Ces chasseurs qui passent dans",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 50,
                    "line_text": "La ville, ont du sang aux dents.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 51,
                    "line_text": "O Balzac ! c'est toi qui trouves",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 52,
                    "line_text": "Ces meurtriers, ces filous ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 53,
                    "line_text": "Nous avons beaucoup de loups,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 54,
                    "line_text": "Et même aussi, quelques louves.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ces chasseurs qui passent dans\nLa ville, ont du sang aux dents.\nO Balzac ! c'est toi qui trouves\nCes meurtriers, ces filous ;\nNous avons beaucoup de loups,\nEt même aussi, quelques louves."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 10,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 55,
                    "line_text": "Sveltes comme des fuseaux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 56,
                    "line_text": "Elles tendent leurs museaux",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 57,
                    "line_text": "De bêtes aventurières,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 58,
                    "line_text": "Et plus d'un sage barbon",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 59,
                    "line_text": "Estime qu'il serait bon",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 60,
                    "line_text": "D'exterminer ces guerrières.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Sveltes comme des fuseaux,\nElles tendent leurs museaux\nDe bêtes aventurières,\nEt plus d'un sage barbon\nEstime qu'il serait bon\nD'exterminer ces guerrières."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 11,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 61,
                    "line_text": "Mais le prudent louvetier",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 62,
                    "line_text": "Veut bien les amnistier,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 63,
                    "line_text": "Si leur candeur les protège ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 64,
                    "line_text": "Et ne soyez pas surpris",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 65,
                    "line_text": "Que ces louves de Paris",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 66,
                    "line_text": "Aient la blancheur de la neige !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Mais le prudent louvetier\nVeut bien les amnistier,\nSi leur candeur les protège ;\nEt ne soyez pas surpris\nQue ces louves de Paris\nAient la blancheur de la neige !"
        }
    ],
    "corpus": "mel"
}